                <p>Monster Hunter Wilds was released in February and it's been a massive success so far, <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/2025-best-selling-games/2900-6281/" data-ref-id="2900-6281">becoming the No. 1 best-selling game of the year in the US months ago</a>. Now, another data point about the game's success has come to light.</p><p>Circana's Mat Piscatella said full-game dollar sales for Wilds are so high that had the game been released in 2024, it would rank as the <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/matpiscatella.bsky.social/post/3lp2oikizps2q" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">No. 6 best-selling game of the year that year.</a> For what it's worth, <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/2024s-best-selling-games-in-the-us/2900-5106/#1" data-ref-id="2900-5106">Madden NFL 25 was the No. 6 best-selling game of 2024 in the US.</a></p>



    
